author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Jon Spencer performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded December 12, 2024.

Songs:
Nothing Can Bring Me Down 00:41
Wrong 02:25
Get Away 04:07
Come Along 06:33
High Gear 09:42
Junk Man 11:10
Disconnected 13:16

Ty Wagner - Guest Vocals

Host: Troy Nelson
Audio & Mastering Engineer: Kevin Suggs

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Leah Franks & Scott Holpainen
